                    <lb /><hi rendition="#i">That's why I bought it</hi>"
                </quote>
            </head>
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_03db0457">
            <p>
                <lb />
                <hi rendition="#k">
                    <hi rendition="#i">T</hi>he
                </hi>
                infinite joy and satisfaction that attend the
                <lb />possession of a thing which is the best of its
                <lb />kind go with the purchase of the
                <name type="brand">
                    Welte-Mignon
                    <lb />Licensee
                    Reproducing Piano
                </name>.
                It brings you the world's
                <lb />finest music, played with all the tone-color, the fire, the
                <lb />verve, the <hi rendition="#i">personality</hi> of the great pianists. You have but
            </p>
